channel.title: [PI] Cache Problems. -- Repping ++
channel.description: Ok, so I have downloaded an rsps non-packaged including a source, client, and cache. I am wanting to change the client background, but that is in the cache and I do not know how to incorporate it within my server files of the source and client.. Repping for help please.

item.title: [PI] Cache Problems. -- Repping ++
item.dc:creator: @wartek wartek
item.description:
@wartek wrote:

Just go to your cache, search the background you got currently , check the heigth and width, make a background with the same heigth, width , name and extension as your previous background and Replace it.
That’s how I do it.
